0.9.name: wordpress/ggis-inline-post
0.9.description: ggis-InlinePost gives authors an easy way to insert a post within a page or another post. Simply add [ggisinlinepost id="id"] to your post. There are a few attributes to control the display of the inlined post's title, content, metadata, and separators.
